(430, 'Arts, Sciences, and Engineering', 'CHI', 102, 'MAIN_COURSE', 'ELEMENTARY CHINESE II', 'This course is the continuation of Chinese 101.  Knowledge of Pinyin is required.  The focus continues to be on developing listening and speaking skills with an increasing emphasis on \nreading and writing in ideographic characters.  It aims to build a vocabulary based on 500 characters.', 6.0, '', 'H1CHI001', 'CHI 101 or equivalent', ''),
