(510, 'Arts, Sciences, and Engineering', 'CLT', 430, 'MAIN_COURSE', 'FILM AS OBJECT', 'The tangible object at the origin of the onscreen image: the social, cultural and historical value of motion pictures and national film cinemas through an understanding of "Film" as an organic object.', 4.0, '', 'H1JPN010', '', 'CLT 230, CLT 430, ENG 258, ENG 458, FMS 243, FMS 443, JPN 207 (P), JPN 407'),
