(754, 'Arts, Sciences, and Engineering', 'ECO', 231, 'MAIN_COURSE', 'ECONOMETRICS', 'The course is an introduction to the application of econometric methods. It covers the basic tools of estimation, inference and forecast of cross-section, time-series and panel data models. ', 4.0, '', ' ', 'Eco 230, Math 203, or Stat 213', ''),
