(756, 'Arts, Sciences, and Engineering', 'ECO', 236, 'MAIN_COURSE', 'HEALTH ECONOMICS', 'Analysis of factors that affect supply and demand in the market for medical care: risk, insurance, externalities, ethics, regulation. ', 4.0, '', 'S1ECO001, S1ECO004, S1HLS002, S1PH002, S1PH004', 'ECO 207', 'ECO 236 (P), ECO 236W'),
