(1205, 'Arts, Sciences, and Engineering', 'MSC', 520, 'MAIN_COURSE', 'SPIN BASED ELECTRONICS', 'Basic physics of magnetism and of quantum mechanical spin. Aspects of spin transport with emphasis on spin-diffusion in semiconductor.', 4.0, '', '', 'Permission of Instructor & familiarity with elementary quantum mechanics', 'ECE 520 (P), MSC 520, PHY 526, TEE 520'),
