(1234, 'Arts, Sciences, and Engineering', 'MTH', 164, 'MAIN_COURSE', 'MULTIDIMENSIONAL CALCULUS', 'Differentiation and linear approximation, extrema, Taylor series.  Line, surface, and volume integrals; coordinate changes, Jacobians.  Divergence theorem, Stokes'' theorem. \n\nThis course uses the Tuesday/Thursday 08:00-09:30am Common Exam time.', 4.0, '', 'N1INT014, N1MTH001, N1MTH003, N1MTH004, N1MTH005', 'MTH 143, 162, or 172.  ( and )', ''),
