(2018, 'Arts, Sciences, and Engineering', 'CAS', 352, 'MAIN_COURSE', 'MTH 162 WORKSHOP LEADERSHIP A', 'This course surveys group dynamics, learning theory and pedagogy. The larger goals for this course are to develop leadership skills, to foster ongoing communication among faculty members and workshop leaders, and to provide an environment for focused review of workshop modules. ', 2.0, '', '', '[A] Instructor''s permission required', ''),
